Title: Basketball Care Package Stickers
Body (HTML):
Turn your delivery into something extraordinary. Our basketball care package sticker kits are printed on sticker paper, come ready to use and require no glue. PLEASE NOTE
◆◆ BOX NOT INCLUDED

Your sticker kit Includes:
- 4 stickers
- Instructions

SIZES

◆Medium Flat Rate Kit:
- Top & Bottom flaps (11" X 4.25”)
- Side flaps (8.25" X 4.25”)
- Covers box flaps only

◆XL Medium Flat Rate Kit:
- Top & Bottom flaps (11" X 6.25”)
- Side flaps (8.25" X 6.25” )
- Covers box flaps and extends below flap

◆Large Flat Rate Kit:
- Top, Bottom and Side flaps (12" X 6")
- Covers box flaps only

◆XL Large Flat Rate Kit:
- Top, Bottom and Side flaps (12" X 8”)
- Covers box flaps and extends below flap

◆10" X 8" Kit:
- Top, Bottom and Side flaps (10" X 8”)

If you do not see the size you need, please contact us to create a custom sticker kit.

Sample show in in Large Flat Rate Size

Medium and large flat rate boxes are a great way to ship your care packages. Visit your local US post office or USPS.com to receive your free flat rate shipping boxes. The box features predetermined rates for domestic packages up to 70 lbs. Priority mail boxes are also a great option for international shipping.
For direct links to order these boxes please feel free to contact me.

Our kits are designed specifically for USPS Medium and Large flat rate boxes, but can be used on some UPS, FedEx and other shipping boxes. Please see more information on sizes below.

PLEASE NOTE
◆◆ BOX NOT INCLUDED

Your sticker kit Includes:
- 4 stickers
- Instructions

SIZES

◆Medium Flat Rate Kit:
- Top & Bottom flaps (11" X 4.25”)
- Side flaps (8.25" X 4.25”)
- Covers box flaps only

◆XL Medium Flat Rate Kit:
- Top & Bottom flaps (11" X 6.25”)
- Side flaps (8.25" X 6.25” )
- Covers box flaps and extends below flap

◆Large Flat Rate Kit:
- Top, Bottom and Side flaps (12" X 6")
- Covers box flaps only

◆XL Large Flat Rate Kit:
- Top, Bottom and Side flaps (12" X 8”)
- Covers box flaps and extends below flap

◆10" X 8" Kit:
- Top, Bottom and Side flaps (10" X 8”)

If you do not see the size you need, please contact us to create a custom sticker kit.

USPS PRIORITY MAIL BOXES

Medium and large flat rate boxes are a great way to ship your care packages. Visit your local US post office or USPS.com to receive your free flat rate shipping boxes. The box features predetermined rates for domestic packages up to 70 lbs. Priority mail boxes are also a great option for international shipping.
